model_metadata.model_description: DP 2025 Q2, 16 layers with dynamic nnei.
A two-layer semi-local GRACE model, pre-fitted on the OMat24 and fine-tuned on sAlex+MPTraj datasets, with fixed 6 Å cutoff.
A multitask trained model, refer to https://huggingface.co/mace-foundations/mace-mh-1.
DP 2025 Q4, 24 layers with dynamic nnei and frame-level parameters to support explicit charge/spin inputs.
